TITLE: Inflation eroded pay by 1.7% over the past year
SUMMARY: Workers have seen their hourly pay jump at about the fastest clip in 15 years. But high annual inflation has eaten into those raises.

TITLE: Billion-year-old black diamond bought with cryptocurrency for $4.3 million
SUMMARY: A billion-year-old black diamond was bought using cryptocurrency in an auction for £3.16 million ($4.3 million).
